<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-good-bad-shape">in good / bad shape</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>身体健康 / 不健康；状态好 / 不好：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s in good shape for a man of his age. 
对他这个年龄的人来说，他这身体算是不错了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The economy is in very bad shape and is likely to get worse. 
经济形势很不好，而且还有可能恶化。</p></div></div>